articles.title: Authorities find "evidence" while searching for missing Australian, American surfers in Mexican region plagued by cartel violence - CBS News
articles.description: Australian brothers Jake and Callum Robinson and their American friend have not been seen since April 27.
articles.content: Mexican authorities said Thursday they have found tents and questioned three people in the case of two Australians and an American who went missing over the weekend in the Pacific coast state of Baja… [+3223 chars]
